parameters: Sage Amakane: "It's finally time to say goodbye... Flora-san."

Sage Amakane: "Summoned to this world so suddenly, battling terrifying
monsters, and embarking on adventures in unfamiliar places... It must
have been very difficult for you."

Sage Amakane: "As the Warrior of Light who saved our world... I can't
even find the words to express my gratitude."

Flora: "I should be the one thanking you. I wish I could come back to
this world again, but that's not possible, is it...?"
Sage Amakane: "Yes, this was a special case among special cases..."

Sage Amakane: "Traveling between different worlds causes great
distortions in space-time, so Flora-san will no longer be able to set
foot in \N[261]."

Flora: "I will never forget any of you. Please take care, Amakane-
sama."
Flora: "Do you remember what I said?"

Flora: "Even though I'll be returning to my original world, what I
said will always hold true..."

Flora: "If anything happens to Liese-chan, I'll cross time and space to
come to your aid."

Flora: "After all, I am the Warrior of Light, so surely I can do at
least that much."

Flora: "The adventures we shared in this world, how you've always been
there to help me... To me, Liese-chan is the most precious and special
person."
Liese: "Yes, surely... We'll definitely meet again."
Sage Amakane: "Magical energy output at maximum!"
Tower Magician: "Magical energy output at maximum...!"
Flora was enveloped in a dazzling light and disappeared from the spot.

Sage Amakane: "I understand. Your role here is finished... Now you can
live your life as you wish."
Sage Amakane: "... That is my greatest wish. Thank you, Liese."
